## M19(3/6): unsafe builtins are allowed inside an unsafe block.
##
## Per GPT-5.5 entry 35: the same `inUnsafeContext()` predicate
## that gates `%x` raw access also gates unsafe builtins. The
## block IS the audit boundary.

sub main()
  x = 42
  unsafe
    y = @ptrCast(x)          # OK: inside unsafe block
    print(y)
